Scaling your Database Instance
==============================

* Scale Compute or memory vertically
* Scale EBS Storage
* Scale With Read Replicas

Example:
=========

* Modify the RDS Instance 
* Change the DB Instance class

When to apply change?:
========================

    - Immediately
    - During Maintenance Window

Before you scale:
=================

    * Correct Licensing Models
    * When to apply the change
    * Storage/CPU are decoupled
    * Multi- AZ
    * Single AZ